

#VarSKIN
---+++ SKIN -- current skin
   * =%<nop>SKIN%= expands the skin search path. For instance, =SKIN= can be set to =catskin, bearskin=.
   * The =SKIN= setting can be overridden using the URL parameter =skin=, such as =?skin=catskin,bearskin=
   * You can also extend the existing skin path using covers - see [[System.VarCOVER.TOPICKEY][COVER]]
   * Syntax: =%<nop>SKIN%=
   * Expands to: =%SKIN%=
   * See [[System.Skins.TOPICKEY]] for more information
   * Related: [[System.SkinBrowser.TOPICKEY]]